videos.description: Virginia forward Jay Huff receives a touch-pass from Ty Jerome and throws down the dunk with ferocity.
videos.headline: Huff rocks rim with right-handed hammer

videos.description: Virginia's full court press forces a turnover as De'Andre Hunter is clear for takeoff, throwing down a monstrous right-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Hunter throws down thunderous tomahawk slam
